237static int
238gm204_gr_init_ctxctl(struct gf100_gr *gr)
239{
240 return 0;
241}
242
243int
244gm204_gr_init(struct gf100_gr *gr)
245{
246 struct nvkm_device *device = gr->base.engine.subdev.device;
247 const u32 magicgpc918 = DIV_ROUND_UP(0x00800000, gr->tpc_total);
248 u32 data[TPC_MAX / 8] = {}, tmp;
249 u8 tpcnr[GPC_MAX];
250 int gpc, tpc, ppc, rop;
251 int i;
252
253 tmp = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x100c80); /*XXX: mask? */
254 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x418880, 0x00001000 | (tmp & 0x00000fff));
255 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x418890, 0x00000000);
256 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x418894, 0x00000000);
257 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x4188b4, nvkm_memory_addr(gr->unk4188b4) >> 8);
258 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x4188b8, nvkm_memory_addr(gr->unk4188b8) >> 8);
259 nvkm_mask(device, 0x4188b0, 0x00040000, 0x00040000);
260
261 /*XXX: belongs in fb */
262 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x100cc8, nvkm_memory_addr(gr->unk4188b4) >> 8);
263 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x100ccc, nvkm_memory_addr(gr->unk4188b8) >> 8);
264 nvkm_mask(device, 0x100cc4, 0x00040000, 0x00040000);
265
266 gf100_gr_mmio(gr, gr->func->mmio);
267
268 gm107_gr_init_bios(gr);
269
270 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(0, 0x3018), 0x00000001);
271
272 memset(data, 0x00, sizeof(data));
273 memcpy(tpcnr, gr->tpc_nr, sizeof(gr->tpc_nr));
274 for (i = 0, gpc = -1; i < gr->tpc_total; i++) {
275 do {
276 gpc = (gpc + 1) % gr->gpc_nr;
277 } while (!tpcnr[gpc]);
278 tpc = gr->tpc_nr[gpc] - tpcnr[gpc]--;
279
280 data[i / 8] |= tpc << ((i % 8) * 4);
281 }
282
283 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x0980), data[0]);
284 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x0984), data[1]);
285 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x0988), data[2]);
286 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x098c), data[3]);
287
288 for (gpc = 0; gpc < gr->gpc_nr; gpc++) {
289 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0914),
290 gr->magic_not_rop_nr << 8 | gr->tpc_nr[gpc]);
291 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0910), 0x00040000 |
292 gr->tpc_total);
293 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0918), magicgpc918);
294 }
295
296 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x3fd4), magicgpc918);
297 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x08ac), nvkm_rd32(device, 0x100800));
298 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_BCAST(0x033c), nvkm_rd32(device, 0x100804));
299
300 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400500, 0x00010001);
301 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400100, 0xffffffff);
302 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x40013c, 0xffffffff);
303 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400124, 0x00000002);
304 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x409c24, 0x000e0000);
305 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x405848, 0xc0000000);
306 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x40584c, 0x00000001);
307 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404000, 0xc0000000);
308 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404600, 0xc0000000);
309 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x408030, 0xc0000000);
310 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x404490, 0xc0000000);
311 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x406018, 0xc0000000);
312 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x407020, 0x40000000);
313 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x405840, 0xc0000000);
314 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x405844, 0x00ffffff);
315 nvkm_mask(device, 0x419cc0, 0x00000008, 0x00000008);
316
317 for (gpc = 0; gpc < gr->gpc_nr; gpc++) {
318 for (ppc = 0; ppc < gr->ppc_nr[gpc]; ppc++)
319 nvkm_wr32(device, PPC_UNIT(gpc, ppc, 0x038), 0xc0000000);
320 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0420), 0xc0000000);
321 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0900), 0xc0000000);
322 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x1028), 0xc0000000);
323 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x0824), 0xc0000000);
324 for (tpc = 0; tpc < gr->tpc_nr[gpc]; tpc++) {
325 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x508), 0xffffffff);
326 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x50c), 0xffffffff);
327 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x224), 0xc0000000);
328 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x48c), 0xc0000000);
329 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x084), 0xc0000000);
330 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x430), 0xc0000000);
331 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x644), 0x00dffffe);
332 nvkm_wr32(device, TPC_UNIT(gpc, tpc, 0x64c), 0x00000005);
333 }
334 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x2c90), 0xffffffff);
335 nvkm_wr32(device, GPC_UNIT(gpc, 0x2c94), 0xffffffff);
336 }
337
338 for (rop = 0; rop < gr->rop_nr; rop++) {
339 nvkm_wr32(device, ROP_UNIT(rop, 0x144), 0x40000000);
340 nvkm_wr32(device, ROP_UNIT(rop, 0x070), 0x40000000);
341 nvkm_wr32(device, ROP_UNIT(rop, 0x204), 0xffffffff);
342 nvkm_wr32(device, ROP_UNIT(rop, 0x208), 0xffffffff);
343 }
344
345 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400108, 0xffffffff);
346 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400138, 0xffffffff);
347 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400118, 0xffffffff);
348 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400130, 0xffffffff);
349 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x40011c, 0xffffffff);
350 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400134, 0xffffffff);
351
352 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x400054, 0x2c350f63);
353
354 gf100_gr_zbc_init(gr);
355
356 return gm204_gr_init_ctxctl(gr);
357}
358
359static const struct gf100_gr_func
360gm204_gr = {
361 .init = gm204_gr_init,
362 .mmio = gm204_gr_pack_mmio,
363 .ppc_nr = 2,
364 .grctx = &gm204_grctx,
365 .sclass = {
366 { -1, -1, FERMI_TWOD_A },
367 { -1, -1, KEPLER_INLINE_TO_MEMORY_B },
368 { -1, -1, MAXWELL_B, &gf100_fermi },
369 { -1, -1, MAXWELL_COMPUTE_B },
370 {}
371 }
372};
373
374int
375gm204_gr_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_gr **pgr)
376{
377 return gf100_gr_new_(&gm204_gr, device, index, pgr);
378}
